sub_title: Lawyer | Partner | Head of Climate Risk and Sustainability bij Houthoff
summary: I'm a lawyer and partner at Houthoff, one of the largest Dutch law firms. I'm specialized in EU and Dutch environmental law and spatial planning law. Within this expertise I advise to and litigate for i.a. (large) industrial companies, investment companies, etc., including for the M&A/transaction practice. I regularly publish and teach about environmental law topics, and am a member of various specialist associations.
